index price deviations, with settlements processed through the hybrid on-chain risk engine. The platform's off-chain sequencer enables rapid position adjustments while maintaining decentralized settlement guarantees. Cross-margin default means funding payments automatically affect overall portfolio PnL without requiring position-specific collateral management. Rate calculations incorporate both spot-perp basis and long-short open interest imbalances across the Vertex orderbook."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
